====================================================
PROJECT CONTEXT — PARLA ITALIANO
====================================================

Parla Italiano is a scenario-based Italian learning application focused on:
- practical survival Italian
- real-world communication
- immersive conversational learning
- A1–A2 learners
- spoken interaction readiness

The app teaches Italian primarily through:
- realistic scenarios
- contextual vocabulary
- spoken phrases
- conversational sentence interaction
- AI tutor conversations
- SRS review systems
- interactive games

The philosophy of the app is:

NOT:
- textbook memorization
- isolated grammar drilling
- robotic educational dialogue

BUT:
- practical communication
- conversational immersion
- real-world survival interaction
- communicative competence
- spoken Italian exposure

The learner should feel:
“I could genuinely survive this situation in Italy.”

====================================================
TECHNICAL CONTEXT
====================================================

The project structure contains scenario folders.

Base directory:

src/data/exports

Example:

src/data/exports/accommodation/apartment_key_pickup/

Each scenario folder contains:
- vocabulary JSON
- phrases JSON
- sentences JSON
- realistic conversation corpus

